metadata.name: YEE
metadata.description:
YEE is an artwork, performance & social experiment

Attendees are invited to digitally engage with the image via Twitter, becoming a part of the performance using the thread to create a virtual event for the unveiling of YEE.wav

Upon collection, YEE and YEE.wav become CC0 public domain

View the thread:
https://twitter.com/JIMMYEDGAR/status/1486113370927415307?s=20
